what is vpc-----
vpc is a virtual private clould------
It is a logically isolated private network in AWS where you can launch and manage cloud resources securely.
_______________________
what is subnet
A subnet is a logical subdivision of a VPC’s IP address range, placed within a specific Availability Zone, 
used to organize resources, control traffic, and launch instances securely.
_____________________
what is public subnet
public subnet has internet access through IGW
__________________
what is private subnet
private sunet access internet through NAT gateway
_______________
what is IGW
IGW is attached to a VPC and, together with route tables, enables public subnets to send and receive traffic from the internet.
_______________________________---
What is NAT
A NAT allows instances in private subnets to access the internet without exposing them to inbound internet traffic.
_____________
what is route table
“A route table tells a subnet where to send its traffic.”
